    tmp = (wp.exp(wp.cos(v2 + 0.10)) * (v1 / (v1 + 0.81 / v0 + 0.35)))
    tmp = wp.exp(0.44)
    v1 = (((v0 + 0.49 / tmp + 0.55) * wp.exp(v1 + 0.59)) / 0.14)
